The death has occurred of Mrs. Mary Aiyegbusi. She died on July 2. She was 93. The deceased was the younger sister to the late Ondo State governor Chief Michael Adekunle Ajasin. She retired as a senior education officer at the Lagos State Ministry of Education and established Mbari Mbayo Group of Schools in Lagos. An active member of St. Lukeâ€™s Military Church, Myoung Barracks, Yaba, Lagos, she was a philanthropist, who assisted in paying the school fees of the less privileged. She is survived by six children, Jide, Kofo, Folarin, Dupe, Tola and Dotun.